From 89380313a0d0444b4d8f05403f581c22a1b18e5f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: SlayZone Dev <dev@slayzone.local>
Date: Sun, 19 Apr 2026 19:47:46 +0200
Subject: [slayzone] slayzone: Phase 7.3 projects webui + SlayzoneProjectsHost

Ports the slim left-rail projects region onto chrome://slayzone-projects/
following the Phase 7.1 StatusBar recipe. Adds:

- chrome/browser/slayzone/mojom/projects.mojom: ProjectsHost with a
  single GetSnapshot() => (ProjectsSnapshot) method. Mirror of the
  outer packages/shared/mojo-bindings/mojom/projects.mojom.
- slayzone_projects_host.{h,cc}: per-SlayzoneBrowserView Mojo impl.
  GetSnapshot forwards to SidecarClient::Call(projects:get-snapshot);
  response dict -> ProjectsSnapshot struct with ProjectEntry list.
- chrome/browser/ui/webui/slayzone/slayzone_projects_ui.{h,cc}:
  chrome://slayzone-projects/ WebUIController. Serves the
  @slayzone/webui-projects Vite bundle from
  --slayzone-webui-bundle-dir/projects/dist/ (inline error page when
  the flag is missing). CSP + bundle-serving + BindInterface mirror
  the Phase 7.1 statusbar pattern verbatim.
- SlayzoneBrowserView: owns a SlayzoneProjectsHost; new projects_host()
  accessor.
- SlayzoneRegionContainer::RegionUrl: routes 'projects' region to the
  dedicated host (replaces the placeholder URL).
- ChromeURLHosts()/webui_url_constants: register
  chrome://slayzone-projects/ host.
- chrome_browser_interface_binders_webui_parts_desktop: registers
  ForWebUI<SlayzoneProjectsUI>().Add<ProjectsHost>().
- BUILD.gn: new .cc/.h files wired into browser + ui targets;
  mojom/BUILD.gn adds projects.mojom.
